"title": "COMPOSITE VENEERS ‚Äî resources",
"body": "resources\n    ‚óè‚Äã Link to \"Diastema Closure Instructions\"\n    ‚óè‚Äã Link to Dr. Baroudi's Veneers Presentation\n    ‚óè‚Äã Link to Dr. Baroudi's Anterior Layering Technique"
