"section": "DENTURES",
"title": "DENTURE STEPS ‚Äî anterior try-in: equipment",
"body": "anterior try-in: equipment\n    ‚óè‚Äã from sterilization: exam kit, waxing kit, lab handpiece, lab burs, Fox plane, occlusal plane, Hanau torch, patient goggles,\n         blood glucose kit\n    ‚óè‚Äã from locker: blood pressure cuff, loupes and/or eye protection, stone spatula, hot plate, trial dentures & articulator\n    ‚óè‚Äã in clinic: Thompson stick, extra-hard baseplate wax\n    ‚óè‚Äã in unit: matches, tongue depressor"
