"title": "MATERIALS",
"body": "Link to Sterilization Kits\n\nLink to Materials List\n\nsummary\n                                 JetSet ‚Äî temporary crown or bridge\n temporary restoration           Integrity ‚Äî temporary crown (no bridge)\n                                 Telio ‚Äî temporary inlay/onlay in digital clinic\n\n temporary bridge                JetSet\n\n temporary direct restoration    IRM (zinc oxide eugenol)\n\n                                 TempBond NE\n temporary cement                UltraTemp\n                                 Durelon\n\n                                 FujiCem ‚Äî RMGI\n permanent cement                RelyX Ultimate ‚Äî resin; for ceramic restorations\n                                 Panavia ‚Äî resin; dual-cure; for digitally-designed ceramic crowns\n\n                                 Renamel Microfill ‚Äî for anterior restorations\n                                 Renamel Nanofill ‚Äî for anterior or posterior restorations\n direct restoration\n                                 Ketac Nano ‚Äî RMGI; for non-stress-bearing areas\n                                 Wave ‚Äî flowable composite; indicated only for small defects & intermediate layer\n\n                                 Gluma ‚Äî dentin desensitizer for cavity or crown prep\n pulp protectors                 Vitrebond ‚Äî RMGI; liner that releases fluoride; not for pulp capping (direct or indirect)\n                                 Dycal (calcium hydroxide) ‚Äî pulp cap (direct or indirect)\n\n core buildup                    Bisco Light-Core ‚Äî comes in blue or natural color\n\n prefabricated post              ParaPost\n\n                                 Viscostat ‚Äî ferric sulfate 20%\n hemorrhage control              Viscostat clear ‚Äî aluminum chloride 25%\n                                 Hemodent ‚Äî buffered aluminum chloride\n\n denture fit evaluation          pressure indicating paste (PIP)\n\n crown (bridge) fit evaluation   fit-checker\n\n denture retention               Fixodent\n\n                                 Coe Comfort ‚Äî tissue conditioner reline material\n denture reline                  Coe Soft ‚Äî soft reline material\n                                 GC Reline ‚Äî hard reline material"
